Package uk.co.michaelshields.assignment_1

Class Member

java.lang.Object
uk.co.michaelshields.assignment_1.Member
All Implemented Interfaces:
uk.co.michaelshields.assignment_1.Displayable, uk.co.michaelshields.assignment_1.IDNumber
public class Member extends Object implements uk.co.michaelshields.assignment_1.Displayable, uk.co.michaelshields.assignment_1.IDNumber
A class that models a member's details. This class utilises:
  • The EmailValidator class of the org.apache.commons.validator.routines lib
  • The PhoneNumberUtil and PhoneNumber classes of the com.google.i18n.phonenumbers lib
The class also implements the Displayable and IDNumber interfaces
Version:
1.0
Author:
M. Shields
